---
const { currentLocale } = Astro;
---

<div
  class="grid w-full items-end overflow-hidden pe-4 pb-4 max-2xl:justify-end 2xl:items-center"
>
  <div
    class="fade grid text-xl font-bold text-balance text-white *:[grid-area:1/1] sm:text-2xl md:text-4xl/[1.3] 2xl:ms-[62vw] 2xl:items-center"
  >
    {
      currentLocale === "ko" ? (
        <>
          <p>
            새로운 금융시장
            <br />
            <br />
            우리가 혁신을 선도 하겠습니다.
          </p>
          <p>
            IT와 블록체인으로 다져진 기업
            <br />
            <br />
            이제,{" "}
            <span class="bg-linear-to-r from-[#e38536] to-[#f5e948] bg-clip-text text-transparent">
              암호화폐거래소
            </span>
            와<br />
            <span class="ps-[4ch]">
              <span class="bg-linear-to-r from-[#D8F3FF] to-[#7DA6FF] bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                디지털뱅크
              </span>
            </span>{" "}
            사업을 시작합니다.
          </p>
          <p>
            글로벌을 향한,
            <br />
            <br />
            혁신적인 금융의 새 지평을
            <br />
            열겠습니다.
          </p>
          <p>
            당신 곁에서,
            <br />
            당신의 손안에서,
            <br />
            가장 신뢰하는
            <br />
            <br />
            당신의 파트너가 되겠습니다.
          </p>
        </>
      ) : (
        <>
          <p>A new era of<br />finance begins.</p>
          <p class="max-w-[20ch]">Built on blockchain innovation - launching <span class="bg-linear-to-r from-[#e38536] to-[#f5e948] bg-clip-text text-transparent">crypto exchange</span> and <span class="bg-linear-to-r from-[#D8F3FF] to-[#7DA6FF] bg-clip-text text-transparent">digital banking</span>.</p>
          <p>Global innovation<br />without borders.</p>
          <p>Your trusted partner,<br />always.</p>
        </>
      )
    }
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .fade > * {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeInOut 20s ease-out infinite;
  }

  .fade > :nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: 5s;
  }
  .fade > :nth-child(3) {
    animation-delay: 10s;
  }
  .fade > :nth-child(4) {
    animation-delay: 15s;
  }

  @keyframes fadeInOut {
    0% {
      translate: 5%;
    }
    5%,
    20% {
      translate: 0;
      opacity: 1;
    }
    25% {
      translate: -5%;
      opacity: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
